ay loss to disfavored portfolios. As alleged, Leech allocated hundreds of m=
illions of dollars of net first-day gains to favored portfolios, which also=
 benefited Leech personally, and a similar amount of net first-day losses t=
o disfavored portfolios.=C2=A0</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"=
