 without telling the applicable broker the specific client for which a trad=
e is intended at the time of the trade.=E2=80=9D And then he=E2=80=99d figu=
re out the allocations later:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">M=
ost of Western Asset=E2=80=99s portfolio managers used its electronic tradi=
